Config may be stored automatically in git:
- every detector generates an 8 bit trigger word
- every possible value has it's own downlscaling factor
- based on all 8 bit words a global L1/L2 word (8 bit) is generated
- detector specifig trigger word should be stored
- reconstructed data should also be stored an reused offline
A special detector ID may be used to store data in output data
